anybadge/issues/14/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/jongracecox/anybadge/issues/14/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/jongracecox/anybadge/issues/14", "id": 445609887, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU0NDU2MDk4ODc=", "number": 14, "title": "Extra padding around long Value text.", "user": {"login": "ahogen", "id": 6827790, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY4Mjc3OTA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/6827790?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen", "html_url": "https://github.com/ahogen", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ahogen/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 6, "created_at": "2019-05-17T20:40:50Z", "updated_at": "2019-06-22T05:03:06Z", "closed_at": "2019-06-01T07:42:37Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Love the library. Been using it a lot!\r\n\r\nI recently had a need/desire to put a long piece of text in a badge and found that there was lots of padding around the value.\r\n\r\n### What I wanted:\r\n\r\n- Badge width: about 280\r\n- Text X: about 170\r\n\r\n![expected](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6827790/57954770-b94a3d80-78a8-11e9-9ee9-e4d1b8394db7.PNG)\r\n\r\n### What `anybadge` actually made:\r\n\r\n- Badge width: 357\r\n- Text X: 210\r\n\r\n![actual]